content:
Some key differences between #Bitcoin and #BitcoinCash:

Bitcoin
- 1MB max block size
- SegWit enabled 
- Leans towards decentralization
- Typically higher fees

Bitcoin Cash
- 8MB max block size
- SegWit not enabled
- More centralized network
- Typically lower fees
